    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "（お腹空いた～！　やっとお昼の時間だよ～）\n（今日はお父さん直伝特製ラーメン弁当！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I'm hungry! Finally lunchtime~）\n（Today's lunch box is a special ramen that I learned from my dad!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "（麺の上に具材を並べて……）\n（わわっ、チャーシュー落としちゃった……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Place the ingredients on top of noodles…）\n（Whoops~‚ I dropped my char siu…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.0333347956,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hit-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2300.000000000001
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 233.33187110000074
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "（誰も私のことなんか見てないし……）\n（ふーふーすればセーフ……だよね？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Because~ no one will see me……）\n（If I blow on it I'll be safe… right?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.1333347956,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.1999981289
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "（ふーふー……。セーフ……！）\n（最後は魔法瓶のスープを注いで……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（PhewーPhew…. Safe…!）\n（Finally~ pour the soup from the thermos…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.1999981289,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6733.337429600002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.9333355585
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "愛ちゃん、愛ちゃん、スープ入れる前に\n机に落としたチャーシューは洗った方がええんちゃう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai-chan~‚ Ai-chan~‚ before you add the soup\nWouldn't it be better to wash the char siu that was dropped on the desk?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.9333355585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "ゆゆゆゆ優ちゃん！？　な、なんでここに！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Y-Y-Y-Yu-chan!? W-Why are you here!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.1000022251,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.1000055584
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.3666696547
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "同じ学校やねんから、そんな驚くこともないやろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We go to the same school~ so it's not that surprising",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.3666696547,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.900003751
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだけど、突然出て来たから……\nいつからいたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true~‚ but it came out of nowhere…\nHow long have you been there?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.900003751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.4666704177
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "鼻歌歌いながらお弁当箱出してる辺りから、かなぁ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Was it~ when you were humming as you took out your lunch box?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.4666704177,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.6666742324
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "なんやラーメンのいい匂いするな～思ったら\n愛ちゃんのお弁当やってん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something smells good like ramen~ I thought\nIt was Ai's lunch box",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.6666742324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.5666742324
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "うっ……授業終わってすぐからですね……\nもっと早く声を掛けてほしかったです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… right after class ended…\nI wish you had told me sooner…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.5666742324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.7000085829
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "だってあまりにも楽しそうにお弁当の準備しとるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because it looked so much fun preparing lunch box",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.7000085829,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.4333378473
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "今日はお父さん直伝のラーメン弁当だったから\nいつも以上にワクワクしちゃいまして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today I made a ramen lunch box using my dad's skills\nI'm more excited than usual…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.4333378473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.1000090915
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、愛ちゃんは可愛らしいな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha~‚ Ai-chan is so cute~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.1000090915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、愛ちゃんのクラスメイトの方ですよね～\nどうも～、いつも応援してくれておおきに～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh~ you're Ai-chan's classmate~\nThank you~~‚ for always supporting me~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.8000106173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.2333449679
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんな～、学校ではサインとか写真はNGなんよ\n来週握手会あるから良かったら遊びに来てな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry~~‚ autographs and photos are not allowed at school\nThere's a handshake event next week~ so please come along if you'd like",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.2333449679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.8000085828
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～、優ちゃんは人気者ですね～。優ちゃんが\nクラスに遊びに来るといつもみーんな注目してます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh~~‚ Yu-chan is really popular~. Whenever Yu~chan\ncomes to visit class~ everyone pays attention!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.8000085828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.1000045137
    },
